com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.services.s3.iterable

Class S3Objects

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.services.s3.iterable.S3Objects
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<S3ObjectSummary>

    public class S3Objects
extends Object
implements Iterable<S3ObjectSummary>
    Provides an easy way to iterate Amazon S3 objects in a "foreach" statement. For example: 
     for ( S3ObjectSummary summary : S3Objects.withPrefix(s3, "my-bucket", "photos/") ) {
     System.out.printf("Object with key '%s'\n", summary.getKey());
 }

    The list of S3ObjectSummarys will be fetched lazily, a page at a time, as they are needed. The size of the page can be controlled with the S3Objects.withBatchSize(int) method.
